OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry throughout with sunniest
OL,7,Fskies across the south. A few showers
OL,8,Fpossible at times, especially in the
OL,9,Fwest. Remaining very warm although
OL,10,Ffresher for a time in the east.
